fields.value: Varietal tracking and impact assessment (Phase II) under the Stress-tolerant Rice in Africa and South Asia

dsDescriptionValue.value: (1)To investigate the farmer-to-farmer seed distribution, we conducted a neighbor survey of farmers who have adopted Swarna-Sub1 rice seeds in Eastern India (Odisha and Uttar Pradesh (2) To analyze the factors that determine the adoption of Swarna-Sub1 (3) To understand the perception of farmers regarding the characteristics of Swarna-Sub1
